text = "[wave amp=8.0 freq=1.5]This game contains content that may [color=#df2020]shock[/color] or [color=#df2020]disturb[/color] some players. Please read the list below before playing:

[color=#cccccc]-> Violence and Gore:[/color] The game features scenes of [color=#df2020]murder[/color], brutal zombie attacks, blood, [color=#df2020]dismemberment[/color], and the use of firearms.

[color=#cccccc]-> Psychological Pressure:[/color] The story and gameplay include [color=#df2020]hallucinations[/color], distortions of reality, disorientation, and an oppressive atmosphere of hopelessness.

[color=#cccccc]-> Scares and Loud Sounds:[/color] The game contains sudden, frightening moments ([color=#df2020]jumpscares[/color]) and loud sound effects.

[color=#cccccc]-> Photosensitivity (Epilepsy):[/color] The game features frequent flashing lights, flashing screens, and strobe effects. If you or someone close to you has an epileptic disorder, consult a doctor before playing.

[color=#aaaaaa]Recommendation: The game is [color=#df2020]not recommended[/color] for individuals with unstable mental states, pregnant women, or minors.[/color][/wave]"
